text: Urvashi Dholakia (born 9 July 1979) is an Indian television actress. She is best known for her role as Komolika Basu in Kasautii Zindagii Kay. == Other websites == * Category:1979 births Category:Indian television actors Category:Indian child actors Category:Punjabi people Category:People from Delhi Category:Living people
